dia.org/resource/Nikola_Joki\\u0107\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nikola_Joki\\u0107\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the legendary LeBron James to the rising star Wembanyama, the Paris 2024 Olympics arguably features the finest collection of global basketball talent to ever take part in the games.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1992, \"end\": 2004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LeBron James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Four-time NBA champion James, 39, will make his Olympic return for Team USA for the first time since London 2012 while his teammate Stephen Curry, the NBA's all-time three-point leader, will make his Olympic debut, aged 36.\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2171, \"end\": 2183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4318121147311926e-15, \"text\": \"NBA champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBA_Finals\"}, {\"begin\": 2184, \"end\": 2189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"score\": 0.9999999999822649, \"rank\": 1.3670131657613932e-11, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LeBron_James\"}, {\"begin\": 2228, \"end\": 2236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.728184769295006e-18, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uni